Events
scroll down
A Special Place to Celebrate
With its uniquely fresh dining experience, picturesque views of nature, and Florida-inspired room decor, West 82° Bar & Grill is a one-of-a-kind venue for events and smaller celebrations in Crystal River. Offer your guests a memorable time by reserving right at the restaurant.
Our Waterfront
Restaurant & Veranda
Accommodates up to 30 guests
From anniversaries to retreats and family getaways, you can reserve our restaurant’s veranda space for a scenic event venue overlooking winding backwaters and blue herons taking flight, made even better by refreshing sips and authentic Florida flavors.
